title: Joe Biden Schedule: Making Videos in Basement, Washing Dishes, Sitting on Porch
description: Democrat presidential front runner Joe Biden said Thursday that his schedule these days regularly consists of sitting in his basement and making videos criticizing President Trump, washing dishes, and sitting on his back porch talking with his grandkids.
